{"tid":898301,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食評]—座銀","createTime":"2018-11-11T14:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T12:36:08.000Z","uid":182683,"like":22,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4bcd3dba74807bbe8ced7ccdcd36f895480adf","tid":898301,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"咁岩去跑馬地搵人，聽個朋友講有間拉麵好正，少有主打雞湯嘅拉麵，試下佢囉！點知食到一肚火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！！我ig有有聲食評片！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-雞白湯拉麵$138<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evwQjca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevwQjca.png&h=6cc41db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n味道：講講個湯底先，因為坐吧枱嘅關系，睇到佢地少少做法，個湯係用左啲類似固體雞油嘅野用攪拌機打混左，個面有堆白泡，顏色好奶白，幾鮮甜同埋幾杰，雞油味好重，唔錯！<br />\n<br />\n到啲麵，失敗！有鹼水味！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個湯已經咁濃味但都仲食到鹼水味，唔掂喎！而且唔多掛湯，質地就正常彈牙。<br />\n<br />\n再講講啲肉，碗野有2塊叉燒同埋2塊雞肉，2款都應該係慢煮同埋冇燒過，叉燒係類似火腿咁嘅薄片，偏瘦冇咩特別；塊雞肉就幾滑多汁同埋好甜，唔錯。<br />\n仲有個堆炸牛蒡幾靚嘅，不過味道冇咩特別。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n價錢：份量正常夠飽但偏貴，雞湯係比較少見，但味道未至於貴過出面啲拉麵。<br />\n<br />\n-A4和牛牛湯拉麵$198<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXmpoD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXmpoD7.png&h=7123ed75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n味道：依碗野唔知咩料！！！除左個幾塊牛肉好食(其實都唔關佢地事,佢地切完冇煮過放上去)，個湯普通牛清湯左啲蔥頭，似史雲生個盒牛湯味，由於個湯係清湯，啲麵食起上黎仲多鹼水味，垃圾！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n價錢：碗野我諗得幾塊牛係值錢，同埋個湯冇咩油，飲埋湯都唔夠飽！！好唔抵！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-溏心蛋1隻$15 <br />\n味道：整得幾好食，應該都係慢煮，好少有個蛋白咁軟身，個黃岩岩好膏狀，中間仲有啲流沙咁嘅口感。<br />\n<br />\n價錢：正常拉麵鋪溏心蛋嘅價錢。<br />\n<br />\n間野幾得意，啲人服務態度極好，會主動問你勁多野同埋推介埋，仲要笑笑口咁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過坐吧枱唔知點解個師傅係咁望住，唔知係咪我太靚仔？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋啲碗同杯幾靚，仲有餐巾同埋濕紙巾比你，服務就唔錯啦但可惜食物唔掂！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwmdgZm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwmdgZm.png&h=01f6e450&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6FEWZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6FEWZn.png&h=78684a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過有樣野真係要讚讚佢，就係個女廁好屈機！！！首先有部獨立冷氣，入面有Handcream,漱口水,髮夾,化妝綿,牙刷牙膏，連m巾都有！！！仲有一堆唔知咩黎，幾貼心嘅。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cissmrb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcissmrb.png&h=0d6f6221&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3C3GqSS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3C3GqSS.png&h=eaeaaf64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVhWZcS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVhWZcS.png&h=4d4e7c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n評分：5/10<br />\n評語：得個廁所值得去<br />\n溝女指數：7/10<br />\n帶囡囡去跑馬地依啲高級地方食野加分！仲要個廁所咁屈！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=trnFlR613oWKJw6Hjw66sARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3b5691a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17168a20c00bdcccb581f782acdceb1effa23b1","tid":898301,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:58:46.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71147275f8011861105d2060a4f71cc994e80